{
  "stem": "1496.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because what Schindler did-- he took over a textile factory in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Actually, this was very close to his home town where he originally came from.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We disassemble, disassemble the textile machinery and start reassemble the munition part-- the munition department.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Work was very hard because we had to unload the machines-- heavy machines-- from the railroad cars.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We had to bring it in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had to even build foundation because the heavy machinery couldn't stay on the floor like this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But even work was very hard, nothing-- Schindler did everything possible to make conditions for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So the factory was on the first floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The second floor was our housing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So actually we lived right in the, on the factory ground.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when we went to work, we had to only go down from the second floor to the first floor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were already in factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They separated, again-- there was a very long building.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they separate the building for women and men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were separated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When the women finally came late in October of 1944-- came from Auschwitz-- that's-- we were there already.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we start assembling the factory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We-- again, don't forget this was almost by the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The rations were very small.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sometimes the Nazis-- the Germans-- couldn't get all the rations what they were assigned.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So, you know, they wouldn't feed the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But again, Schindler was going out-- knowing the territory well because he was from this area.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was going out, buying food on the black market, bringing in to the camp, that we have enough, you know, to keep us alive.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Even once, he found out that there is a dead horse somewhere in the field.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
